item.title: About Me
item.description: My name is Tingshuang (Irene) Tan, first year accounting reserach professional at University of Chicago. I had my BBA(Acc&Fin) and MEcon at University of Hong Kong. I will be applying the Ph.D of Accounting this Fall. Hola！这里是谭婷双的小主页。就如你所见，现在这里空空如也。不过请敬请期待吧:)
